{"id":10,"parent_id":2,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":10,"title":"Matthew 8","subtitle":"","short_title":"Matt.","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/8","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 8"],[".studySummary",["i","Jesus heals a leper, cures the centurion’s servant and others, stills the tempest, and casts out devils—The devils enter a herd of swine."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/8.1","order":"03.03.008.1008"},["b","1"],"When he was come down from the mountain, great multitudes followed him."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/8.2","order":"03.03.008.1009"},["b","2"],"And, behold, there came a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"leper"],"and worshipped him, saying, Lord, if thou wilt, thou canst make me clean."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/8.3","order":"03.03.008.1010"},["b","3"],"And Jesus put forth",["i","his"],"hand, and touched him, saying, I will; be thou clean. And immediately his leprosy was",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"cleansed"],"."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/8.4","order":"03.03.008.1011"},["b","4"],"And Jesus saith unto him, See thou tell no man; but go thy way, shew thyself to the priest, and offer the gift that Moses commanded, for a testimony unto them."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/8.5","order":"03.03.008.1012"},["b","5"],"¶And when Jesus was entered into Capernaum, there came unto him a centurion, beseeching him,"],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/8.6","order":"03.03.008.1013"},["b","6"],"And saying, Lord, my",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"servant"],"lieth at home sick of the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"palsy"],", grievously tormented."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/8.7","order":"03.03.008.1014"},["b","7"],"And Jesus saith unto him, I will come and heal him."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/8.8","order":"03.03.008.1015"},["b","8"],"The centurion answered and said, Lord, I am not",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"worthy"],"that thou shouldest come under my roof: but speak the word only, and my servant shall be",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"healed"],"."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/8.9","order":"03.03.008.1016"},["b","9"],"For I am a man under",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"authority"],", having soldiers under me: and I say to this",["i","man,"],"Go, and he goeth; and to another, Come, and he cometh; and to my servant, Do this, and he doeth",["i","it."]],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/8.10","order":"03.03.008.1017"},["b","10"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"When Jesus"],"heard",["i","it,"],"he marvelled, and said to them that followed, Verily I say unto you, I have not found so great",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"faith"],", no, not in Israel."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/8.11","order":"03.03.008.1018"},["b","11"],"And I say unto you, That",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"many"],"shall come from the east and west, and shall sit down with Abraham, and Isaac, and Jacob, in the kingdom of heaven."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/8.12","order":"03.03.008.1019"},["b","12"],"But the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"children"],"of the kingdom shall be cast out into",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_12b"},"outer darkness"],": there shall be",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_12c"},"weeping"],"and gnashing of teeth."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/8.13","order":"03.03.008.1020"},["b","13"],"And Jesus said unto the centurion, Go thy way; and as thou hast believed,",["i","so"],"be it done unto thee. And his servant was healed in the selfsame hour."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/8.14","order":"03.03.008.1021"},["b","14"],"¶And when Jesus was come into Peter’s house, he saw his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"wife’s"],"mother",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"laid"],", and sick of a fever."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/8.15","order":"03.03.008.1022"},["b","15"],"And he",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"touched"],"her hand, and the fever left her: and she arose, and ministered unto them."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/8.16","order":"03.03.008.1023"},["b","16"],"¶When the even was come, they brought unto him many that were possessed with",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"devils"],": and he cast out the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_16b"},"spirits"],"with",["i","his"],"word, and",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_16c"},"healed"],"all that were sick:"],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/8.17","order":"03.03.008.1024"},["b","17"],"That it might be fulfilled which was spoken by Esaias the prophet, saying,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"Himself"],"took our",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_17b"},"infirmities"],", and bare",["i","our"],["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_17c"},"sicknesses"],"."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/8.18","order":"03.03.008.1025"},["b","18"],"¶Now when Jesus saw great multitudes about him, he gave commandment to depart unto the other side."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/8.19","order":"03.03.008.1026"},["b","19"],"And a certain scribe came, and said unto him, Master, I will",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"follow"],"thee whithersoever thou goest."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/8.20","order":"03.03.008.1027"},["b","20"],"And Jesus saith unto him, The foxes have holes, and the birds of the air",["i","have"],"nests; but the Son of man hath not where to lay",["i","his"],"head."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/8.21","order":"03.03.008.1028"},["b","21"],"And another of his disciples said unto him, Lord,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"suffer"],"me first to go and bury my father."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/8.22","order":"03.03.008.1029"},["b","22"],"But Jesus said unto him,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"Follow"],"me; and let the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_22b"},"dead"],"bury their dead."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/8.23","order":"03.03.008.1030"},["b","23"],"¶And when he was entered into a ship, his disciples followed him."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/8.24","order":"03.03.008.1031"},["b","24"],"And, behold, there arose a great",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"tempest"],"in the sea, insomuch that the ship was covered with the waves: but he was asleep."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/8.25","order":"03.03.008.1032"},["b","25"],"And his disciples came to",["i","him,"],"and awoke him, saying, Lord, save us: we perish."],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/8.26","order":"03.03.008.1033"},["b","26"],"And he saith unto them, Why are ye",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_26a"},"fearful"],", O ye of little faith? Then he arose, and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_26b"},"rebuked"],"the winds and the sea; and there was a great calm."],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/8.27","order":"03.03.008.1034"},["b","27"],"But the men marvelled, saying, What manner of man is this, that even the winds and the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_27a"},"sea"],"obey him!"],["div",{"id":"28","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/8.28","order":"03.03.008.1035"},["b","28"],"¶And when he was come to the other side into the country of the Gergesenes, there met him two possessed with",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_28a"},"devils"],", coming out of the tombs, exceeding fierce, so that no man might pass by that way."],["div",{"id":"29","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/8.29","order":"03.03.008.1036"},["b","29"],"And, behold, they cried out, saying, What have we to do with thee, Jesus, thou Son of God? art thou come hither to torment us before",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_29a"},"the time"],"?"],["div",{"id":"30","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/8.30","order":"03.03.008.1037"},["b","30"],"And there was a good way off from them an herd of many swine feeding."],["div",{"id":"31","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/8.31","order":"03.03.008.1038"},["b","31"],"So the devils besought him, saying, If thou cast us out, suffer us to go away into the herd of swine."],["div",{"id":"32","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/8.32","order":"03.03.008.1039"},["b","32"],"And he said unto them, Go. And when they were come out, they went into the herd of swine: and, behold, the whole herd of swine ran violently down a steep place into the sea, and perished in the waters."],["div",{"id":"33","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/8.33","order":"03.03.008.1040"},["b","33"],"And they that kept them fled, and went their ways into the city, and told every thing, and what was befallen to the possessed of the devils."],["div",{"id":"34","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/8.34","order":"03.03.008.1041"},["b","34"],"And, behold, the whole city came out to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_34a"},"meet"],"Jesus: and when they saw him, they besought",["i","him"],"that he would depart out of their",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_34b"},"coasts"],"."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/8.2a","order":"03.03.008.1042"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/leprosy"},"TG Leprosy"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/8.3a","order":"03.03.008.1044"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/miracle"},"TG Miracle"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/8.6a","order":"03.03.008.1046"},["b","6a"],["span.small","GR"],"child, servant, son; see",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/4.43-54"},"John 4:43–54"],"."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/8.6b","order":"03.03.008.1048"},["b","6b"],["span.small","GR"],"paralysis."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/8.8a","order":"03.03.008.1050"},["b","8a"],["span.small","GR"],"fit, qualified."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/8.8b","order":"03.03.008.1052"},["b","8b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/heal"},"TG Heal"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/8.9a","order":"03.03.008.1054"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/authority"},"TG Authority"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/8.10a","order":"03.03.008.1056"},["b","10a"],["span.small","JST"],"Matt. 8:9",["i","And when they that followed him, heard this, they marveled. And"],"when Jesus …"],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/8.10b","order":"03.03.008.1058"},["b","10b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/17.8.5-20"},"3 Ne. 17:8 (5–20)"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/8.11a","order":"03.03.008.1060"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/13.29.28-30"},"Luke 13:29 (28–30)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/10.45"},"Acts 10:45"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/10.18.9-18"},"2 Ne. 10:18 (9–18)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/45.9"},"D&C 45:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/8.12a","order":"03.03.008.1062"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/30.2"},"2 Ne. 30:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"12b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/8.12b","order":"03.03.008.1064"},["b","12b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.13.1-14"},"Matt. 22:13 (1–14)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/77.8"},"D&C 77:8"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/133.72"},"133:72"],"."],["div",{"id":"12c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/8.12c","order":"03.03.008.1066"},["b","12c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/65.14"},"Isa. 65:14"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/13.42"},"Matt. 13:42"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/19.20"},"Rev. 19:20"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/112.24"},"D&C 112:24"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/8.14a","order":"03.03.008.1068"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9.5"},"1 Cor. 9:5"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-tim/4.3"},"1 Tim. 4:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"14b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/8.14b","order":"03.03.008.1070"},["b","14b"],["span.small","GR"],"lying sick and feverish."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/8.15a","order":"03.03.008.1072"},["b","15a"],["span.small","GR"],"took hold of."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/8.16a","order":"03.03.008.1074"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/4.24"},"Matt. 4:24"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/9.32.32-34"},"9:32 (32–34)"],"."],["div",{"id":"16b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/8.16b","order":"03.03.008.1076"},["b","16b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/spirits-evil-or-unclean"},"TG Spirits, Evil or Unclean"],"."],["div",{"id":"16c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/8.16c","order":"03.03.008.1078"},["b","16c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/heal"},"TG Heal"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/8.17a","order":"03.03.008.1080"},["b","17a"],["span.small","GR"],"He Himself."],["div",{"id":"17b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/8.17b","order":"03.03.008.1082"},["b","17b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-atonement-through"},"TG Jesus Christ, Atonement through"],"."],["div",{"id":"17c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/8.17c","order":"03.03.008.1084"},["b","17c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sickness"},"TG Sickness"],"."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/8.19a","order":"03.03.008.1086"},["b","19a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/9.57"},"Luke 9:57"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/31.10.10-13"},"2 Ne. 31:10 (10–13)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/moro/7.11"},"Moro. 7:11"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/4.3"},"D&C 4:3"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/56.2"},"56:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/8.21a","order":"03.03.008.1088"},["b","21a"],["span.small","GR"],"let, allow."],["div",{"id":"22a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/8.22a","order":"03.03.008.1090"},["b","22a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/commitment"},"TG Commitment"],"."],["div",{"id":"22b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/8.22b","order":"03.03.008.1092"},["b","22b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/death"},"TG Death"],"."],["div",{"id":"24a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/8.24a","order":"03.03.008.1094"},["b","24a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jonah/1.4"},"Jonah 1:4"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/18.13.9-13"},"1 Ne. 18:13 (9–13)"],"."],["div",{"id":"26a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/8.26a","order":"03.03.008.1096"},["b","26a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/courage"},"TG Courage"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/fearful"},"Fearful"],"."],["div",{"id":"26b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/8.26b","order":"03.03.008.1098"},["b","26b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/65.7"},"Ps. 65:7"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/89.9"},"89:9"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/107.29"},"107:29"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-power-of"},"TG God, Power of"],"."],["div",{"id":"27a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/8.27a","order":"03.03.008.1100"},["b","27a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.16.8-17"},"Hel. 12:16 (8–17)"],"."],["div",{"id":"28a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/8.28a","order":"03.03.008.1102"},["b","28a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/spirits-evil-or-unclean"},"TG Spirits, Evil or Unclean"],"."],["div",{"id":"29a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/8.29a","order":"03.03.008.1104"},["b","29a"],["span.small","GR"],"the appointed hour."],["div",{"id":"34a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/8.34a","order":"03.03.008.1106"},["b","34a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/12.18"},"John 12:18"],"."],["div",{"id":"34b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/8.34b","order":"03.03.008.1108"},["b","34b"],["span.small","GR"],"lands, regions."]]}
